 p The  a href="http:/ ublib.boulder.ibm.com/infocenter/wasinfo/v7r0/topic/com.ibm.websphere.express.iseries.doc/info/iseriesexp/ae/tjmx_extend.html" rel="nofollow" 'Extending the WebSphere Application Server administrative system with custom MBeans' document /a  in IBM's infocenter suggests that standard MBeans that have been tested in applications outside WAS should just work.       

 p IBM do state that the UserTransaction lookup is not available to:    

 ul  
 li  p CMT Enterprise beans `http:/ ublib.boulder.ibm.com/infocenter/wasinfo/v7r0/index.jsp?topic=/com.ibm.websphere.base.doc/info/aes/ae/cjta_glotran.html    /li  
