 p Here are some code snippets to perform the requested fucntions:    

 p First you need a queue manager connection ( code qmgr /code ). Then you can create a  code PCFMessageAgent /code :    

 pre  code // Create PCF Message Agent 
try { 
    pcfAgent = new PCFMessageAgent(qmgr); 
