 /code   re  

 p Any help would be greatly appreciated.

p strong This is what I have done: /strong
ol li Following this a href="http://ocpsoft.com/java/jsf2-java/jsf2-how-to-add-the-magic-of-el-el2-to-jsf/" rel="nofollow" post from Lincoln Baxter /a I downloaded el-api-2.2.jar and el-impl-2.2.jar /li li Then created isolated shard library and added them there. /li li p We are using Myfaces so in web.xml added this bit
